     <h1>
      Protecting Human Subjects
     </h1>
     <!-- node.tpl.php -->
     <article about="/protecting-human-subjects" class="node node-page " role="article" typeof="sioc:Item foaf:Document">
      <span class="rdf-meta element-hidden" content="Protecting Human Subjects" property="dc:title">
      </span>
      <span class="rdf-meta element-hidden" content="0" datatype="xsd:integer" property="sioc:num_replies">
      </span>
      <footer class="article-meta">
      </footer>
      <div class="content">
       <span class="print-link">
        <span class="print_html">
         <a class="print-page" href="http://irb.ucsf.edu/print/1" onclick="window.open(this.href); return false" rel="nofollow" title="Display a printer-friendly version of this page.">
          <img alt="Print" class="print-icon print-icon-margin" src="http://irb.ucsf.edu/sites/all/modules/contrib/print/icons/print_icon.png" title="Print" typeof="foaf:Image"/>
          Print
         </a>
        </span>
        <span class="print_pdf">
         <a class="print-pdf" href="http://irb.ucsf.edu/printpdf/1" rel="nofollow" title="Display a PDF version of this page.">
          <img alt="PDF" class="print-icon print-icon-margin" src="http://irb.ucsf.edu/sites/all/modules/contrib/print/print_pdf/icons/pdf_icon.png" title="PDF" typeof="foaf:Image"/>
          PDF
         </a>
        </span>
       </span>
       <div class="field field-type-text-with-summary field-name-body">
        <p>
        </p>
        <h4>
         Click
         <strong>
          <a href="https://irb.ucsf.edu/sites/hrpp.ucsf.edu/files/convert%20application%20guidance.pdf" target="_blank">
           here
          </a>
         </strong>
         for guidance on what to do if you see this pop-up in your IRB application.
        </h4>
        <p class="webedit-aligncenter">
         <img alt="new form version" src="https://irb.ucsf.edu/sites/hrpp.ucsf.edu/files/new%20form%20version.png"/>
        </p>
        <p class="webedit-aligncenter">
         <img alt="HRPP word cloud" height="227" src="http://irb.ucsf.edu/sites/hrpp.ucsf.edu/files/word-cloud-ucsf.png" style="border: 0;" width="354"/>
        </p>
        <p>
         The Human Research Protection Program (HRPP) reviews and monitors research involving human subjects at UCSF and several affiliate institutions to ensure the ethical and equitable treatment of the research subjects. Read more about the
         <a href="/program-description">
          HRPP program
         </a>
         .
        </p>
        <p>
         The HRPP is comprised of these groups:
        </p>
        <ul>
         <li>
          The
          <a href="/irb-review">
           Institutional Review Board (IRB)
          </a>
          , which reviews
          <a href="/research-needing-irb-review">
           human subject research studies
          </a>
          —
          <a href="/submissions">
           learn how to apply to the IRB
          </a>
          ,
         </li>
         <li>
          The
          <a href="/monitoring">
           Quality Improvement Unit (QIU)
          </a>
          , which conducts
          <a href="/monitoring">
           monitoring
          </a>
          ,
          <a href="/training">
           education
          </a>
          and
          <a href="/node/426">
           other QI activities
          </a>
          , and
         </li>
         <li>
          The
          <a href="/stem-cell" style="line-height: 1.538em;">
           Human Gamete, Embryo and Stem Cell Research (GESCR) Committee
          </a>
          .
         </li>
        </ul>
       </div>
       <div class="field field-type-datetime field-name-field-date-published">
        <label>
         Page last updated:
        </label>
        <time content="2019-02-19T00:00:00-08:00" datatype="xsd:dateTime" datetime="2019-02-19T00:00:00-08:00" property="dc:date">
         Feb 19, 2019
        </time>
       </div>
      </div>
     </article>
    </div>
    <!--/main-->
    <div class="sidebar-first col">
     <div class="block block-block ">
      <h2 class="title">
       Common Rule
      </h2>
      <p>
       <a href="https://irb.ucsf.edu/common-rule" target="_blank">
        <div class="media media-element-container media-quarter _none">
         <picture class="media-element file-quarter">
          <!--[if IE 9]><video style="display: none;"><![endif]-->
          <source media="(min-width: 830px)" srcset="/sites/hrpp.ucsf.edu/files/styles/starter_kit_quarter/public/common%20rule%20changes_0.png?itok=B-DyGsv3&amp;timestamp=1547850437 1x"/>
          <source media="(min-width: 380px)" srcset="/sites/hrpp.ucsf.edu/files/styles/starter_kit_sixth/public/common%20rule%20changes_0.png?itok=aii_EJef&amp;timestamp=1547850437 1x"/>
          <source media="(min-width: 277px)" srcset="/sites/hrpp.ucsf.edu/files/styles/starter_kit_quarter/public/common%20rule%20changes_0.png?itok=B-DyGsv3&amp;timestamp=1547850437 1x"/>
          <source media="(min-width: 0px)" srcset="/sites/hrpp.ucsf.edu/files/styles/starter_kit_sixth/public/common%20rule%20changes_0.png?itok=aii_EJef&amp;timestamp=1547850437 1x"/>
          <!--[if IE 9]></video><![endif]-->
          <img alt="" class="media-element file-quarter" src="https://irb.ucsf.edu/sites/hrpp.ucsf.edu/files/styles/starter_kit_quarter/public/common%20rule%20changes_0.png?itok=B-DyGsv3&amp;timestamp=1547850437" title=""/>
         </picture>
        </div>
       </a>
      </p>
      <p>
       Guidelines and tools will be added daily. Check the
       <a href="https://irb.ucsf.edu/common-rule" target="_blank">
        Common Rule
       </a>
       page for updates.
      </p>
      <h2>
      </h2>
     </div>
     <div class="block block-block callout-box ">
      <h2 class="title">
       NIH sIRB Mandate
      </h2>
      <p>
       <a href="/nih-single-irb-mandate">
        <div class="media media-element-container media-square-third _none">
         <picture class="media-element file-square-third">
          <!--[if IE 9]><video style="display: none;"><![endif]-->
          <source media="(min-width: 896px)" srcset="/sites/hrpp.ucsf.edu/files/styles/starterkit_square_third/public/NIH%20sIRB%20Mandate.png?itok=qEByF-4U&amp;timestamp=1515186869 1x"/>
          <source media="(min-width: 604px)" srcset="/sites/hrpp.ucsf.edu/files/styles/starterkit_square_quarter/public/NIH%20sIRB%20Mandate.png?itok=34iySiN9&amp;timestamp=1515186869 1x"/>
          <source media="(min-width: 380px)" srcset="/sites/hrpp.ucsf.edu/files/styles/starterkit_square_sixth/public/NIH%20sIRB%20Mandate.png?itok=P_QcLhTg&amp;timestamp=1515186869 1x"/>
          <source media="(min-width: 277px)" srcset="/sites/hrpp.ucsf.edu/files/styles/starterkit_square_third/public/NIH%20sIRB%20Mandate.png?itok=qEByF-4U&amp;timestamp=1515186869 1x"/>
          <source media="(min-width: 187px)" srcset="/sites/hrpp.ucsf.edu/files/styles/starterkit_square_quarter/public/NIH%20sIRB%20Mandate.png?itok=34iySiN9&amp;timestamp=1515186869 1x"/>
          <source media="(min-width: 0px)" srcset="/sites/hrpp.ucsf.edu/files/styles/starterkit_square_sixth/public/NIH%20sIRB%20Mandate.png?itok=P_QcLhTg&amp;timestamp=1515186869 1x"/>
          <!--[if IE 9]></video><![endif]-->
          <img alt="NIH Single IRB Mandate at UCSF" class="media-element file-square-third" src="http://irb.ucsf.edu/sites/hrpp.ucsf.edu/files/styles/starterkit_square_third/public/NIH%20sIRB%20Mandate.png?itok=qEByF-4U&amp;timestamp=1515186869" title=""/>
         </picture>
        </div>
       </a>
      </p>
      <ul>
       <li>
        <strong>
         <a href="mailto:SingleIRB@ucsf.edu?subject=Single%20IRB%20Consultation%20Request&amp;body=Title%20of%20study%3A%0A%0AUCSF%20PI%20name%3A%20%0A%0APrime%20awardee%20institution%3A%0A%0AIs%20this%20project%20NIH%20funded%3F%20If%20so%2C%20what%20type%20of%20grant%20is%20it%3F%0A%0ANew%20proposal%20or%20competitive%20renewal%3A%0AIf%20renewal%2C%20what%20is%20the%20IRB%20%23%3F%0A%20%0AGrant%20submission%20deadline%3A%0A%0ARisk%20level%3A%20minimal%20or%20greater%20than%20minimal%20risk%0A%0ANumber%20of%20sites%3A%0A%0AName%20of%20each%20outside%20site%3A%0A%0AName%20of%20the%20institution%20are%20you%20requesting%20to%20serve%20as%20the%20Reviewing%20IRB%3A%0A%0AAre%20all%20relying%20sites%20engaged%20in%20human%20subjects%20research%3F%20(Please%20see%20our%20guidance%20here%3A%20http%3A%2F%2Firb.ucsf.edu%2Fresearch-needing-irb-review)%0A%0AIs%20each%20site%20conducting%20the%20exactly%20same%20protocol%20and%20study%20procedures%3F%0A%0ANumber%20of%20unique%20consent%20forms%20(i.e.%20main%20consent%2C%20parental%20permission%2C%20assent%2C%20control%20group%20consent%2C%20etc)%3A%0A%0ABriefly%20describe%20your%20staffing%20capacity%20to%20coordinate%20and%20manage%20all%20IRB%20submissions%2C%20document%20reviews%2C%20event%20reporting%20and%20communication%20between%20sites%3A">
          Click here to contact us at least 60 days prior to grant submission
         </a>
        </strong>
        to discuss the selection of a single IRB.
       </li>
       <li>
        <a href="/nih-single-irb-mandate">
         Read our guidance about the new NIH Single IRB Mandate
        </a>
        .
       </li>
      </ul>
     </div>
